<h3 id="box3-min-vector3-max-vector3" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#box3-min-vector3-max-vector3" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Box3( min : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>, max : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> )</h3>
