<h3 id="min-vector3" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#min-vector3" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">min<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h3>
