<h3 id="clone-box3" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#clone-box3" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.clone" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">clone<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> () : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Box3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h3>
