<h3 id="copy-box-box3-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#copy-box-box3-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.copy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">copy<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( box : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Box3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
