<h3 id="distancetopoint-point-vector3-float" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#distancetopoint-point-vector3-float" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.distanceToPoint" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">distanceToPoint<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( point : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : Float</h3>
