<h3 id="expandbyobject-object-object3d-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#expandbyobject-object-object3d-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.expandByObject" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">expandByObject<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( object : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/core/Object3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Object3D<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
