<h3 id="expandbyscalar-scalar-float-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#expandbyscalar-scalar-float-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.expandByScalar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">expandByScalar<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( scalar : Float ) : this</h3>
