<p>返回包围盒的宽度，高度，和深度。</p>
<h3 id="intersect-box-box3-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#intersect-box-box3-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.intersect" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">intersect<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( box : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Box3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
