<h3 id="intersectstriangle-triangle-triangle-boolean" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#intersectstriangle-triangle-triangle-boolean" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.intersectsTriangle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">intersectsTriangle<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( triangle : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Triangle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Triangle<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : Boolean</h3>
<p><a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Triangle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">triangle<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> - 用来检测是否相交的三角形 <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Triangle" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Triangle<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>。</p>
