<h3 id="set-min-vector3-max-vector3-this" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#set-min-vector3-max-vector3-this" aria-hidden="true">#</a> .<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Box3.set" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">set<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ( min : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>, max : <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> ) : this</h3>
<p><a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">min<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> - <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 表示下边界每个纬度（x,y,z）的值。
<a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">max<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> - <a href="https://threejs.org/docs/index.html#api/zh/math/Vector3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Vector3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 表示上边界每个纬度（x,y,z）的值。</p>
